e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247841582da9d410302d866e38a13824b8981ab5","tid":1815916,"uid":80700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"仆街cctvb"},{"pid":"f61ded0426733847d76ce6e77a38f60f9fe71d9b","tid":1815916,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:18:16.000Z","msg":"衰過亞視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8ddede01285c6e3e0aa4bfd5fd9969361a7038","tid":1815916,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:36:53.000Z","msg":"「請不要把政治事件帶到公司」，「請不要把政治帶來學校」，公司或學校是政治中立。<br />\n同「一國兩制」都是天下最大笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}